- Hour Mode (left button): 
	- press and maintain set button than {
			Hour (0 to 23): press the Left button to add 1 hour / press the Middle button to sub 1 hour.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting minutes.
			Minute (0 to 59): press the Left button to add 1 minutes / press the Middle button to sub 1 minute.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting DOW (day of week).
			DOW (sund to suter): press the Left button to switch to the next day / press the Middle button to go back.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting day of month.
			Day (1 to 31): press the Left button to add 1 day / press the Middle button to sub 1 day.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting months.
			Month (1 to 12): press the Left button to add 1 month / press the Middle button to sub 1 month.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting years.
			YEAR (2000 to 2099): press the Left button to add 1 year / press the Middle button to sub 1 year.
	}

- Alarm Mode (Alarm button): 
	- press and maintain set button than {
			Hour (0 to 23): press the Left button to add 1 hour / press the Middle button to sub 1 hour.
			
			Next : press the Right button to move cursor for setting minutes.
			Minute (0 to 59): press the Left button to add 1 minutes / press the Middle button to sub 1 minute.
			
			Finish : press the Alarm button to save.
	}

- Stopwatch Mode (Middle button):
	- press and maintain set button than {
			Start/Stop: press the Left button to start or to stop the stopwatch.
			Lapse Time: press the Middle button when stopwatch is running.
			Reset: press the Middle button to reset the stopwatch when it is stopped.
	}
	
- Timer Mode (right button):
	- press and maintain set button than {
			Start/Reset: press the Left button to start or to reset the timer.
			Set timer: press the Middle button to adjust the total time (1 to 99 minutes).
			Next Mode: press the Right button to move to Hour mode.
	}	
	
	
- Notes:
		When the countdown time is completed, a buzzer starts a warning sound (same for Alarm).
		When the lapse time is completed, a buzzer		

